advisories: Frequent/Intense Alcohol, Tobacco, or Drug Use or References
description:
Add the excitement of Hollywood-style special effects to your videos and photos with the Coors Light Cold FX app.

The action begins as soon as you choose from one of the super cold effects. Simply use a video or photo you already have on your phone, or take a new one, then choose which effect will provide maximum refreshment. There’s everything from flying Hotstronauts to the earth-shattering ‘Major Impact’.

And it’s easy to save your creations, and then share them with friends on Facebook, Twitter, email or text.

Due to the references to alcohol, Apple classifieds this app as 17+. However, since the application is sponsored by the Coors Brewing Company, by downloading it you state that you are over the age of 21.
releaseNotes:
• Adds 16 oz Coors Light Aluminum Pint video effects into your own videos, with the ability to adjust timing, preview and share.
• Adds ability to Tweet and share via email and Facebook. 
• Seven new photo choices available including Hotstronauts and Ice Cube.
